{% comment %}
==================================================
SHELZY'S DESIGNS - VERCEL WEB ANALYTICS
==================================================

Vercel Web Analytics snippet for Shopify stores.

This snippet provides real-time analytics and insights about visitor behavior,
including page views, device info, and conversion funnel tracking.

Features:
- Real-time analytics dashboard
- Zero JS overhead (optimized script)
- Privacy-friendly tracking (no cookies)
- Automatic event tracking
- Custom event support

Usage:
1. Add this snippet to your theme's <head> section in theme.liquid:
   {% render 'shelzys-vercel-analytics' %}

2. To track custom events, use the webVitals API:
   window.va?.event('event_name', { property: 'value' })

Documentation:
- https://vercel.com/docs/concepts/analytics
- https://vercel.com/docs/concepts/analytics/events-api

==================================================
{% endcomment %}

<!-- Vercel Web Analytics -->
<script defer src="/_vercel/insights/script.js"></script>

{% if request.page_title %}
  {% comment %}
  Optional: Track page title changes for dynamic content
  This helps with analyzing behavior on collection and product pages
  {% endcomment %}
  <script>
    if (window.va) {
      window.va.track = window.va.track || function() {};
    }
  </script>
{% endif %}
